that was in <i>The</i>
<i>Adventures of Nik√©</i> ?

00:00:30.238 --> 00:00:32.240 position:50% align:center
Either they've been
released from custody,

00:00:32.323 --> 00:00:33.992 position:50% align:center
or maybe there's
a copycat group?

