Oh, yes.

00:00:38.163 --> 00:00:39.080 position:50% align:center
It sounds like the group
that called themselves

00:00:39.164 --> 00:00:41.374 position:50% align:center
the "Curio Company" is back.

00:00:41.458 --> 00:00:43.043 position:50% align:center
[HOUSEWIFE 11C] I thought
we got rid of them for good

00:00:43.126 --> 00:00:44.085 position:50% align:center
a long time ago.

00:00:44.169 --> 00:00:45.754 position:50% align:center
I wonder if my
husband will be okay.

00:00:45.837 --> 00:00:46.838 position:50% align:center
