in <i>The Adventures of Nik√©</i> .

00:23:44.174 --> 00:23:47.135 position:50% align:center
And while I've always loved
them, I also imagined that

00:23:47.218 --> 00:23:50.013 position:50% align:center
my story would be
a lot longer than that.

00:23:50.096 --> 00:23:51.931 position:50% align:center
That's why...

00:23:52.015 --> 00:23:53.933 position:50% align:center
In the country where
Miss Fran and Sheila

00:23:54.017 --> 00:23:56.936 position:50% align:center
were able to finally be
honest with each other,

00:23:57.020 --> 00:24:00.440 position:50% align:center
I discovered something
about myself, too.

00:24:00.523 --> 00:24:04.861 position:50% align:center
I want to keep going,
to keep being the Ashen Witch.

00:24:04.944 --> 00:24:08.490 position:50% align:center
An ordinary traveler,
